statements: SELECT * FROM ImpactData WHERE impact_metric = 'Social'
SELECT program_name, community_name FROM ImpactData WHERE impact_value > 100
SELECT community_name, impact_metric, impact_value FROM ImpactData WHERE program_name = 'Education'
SELECT * FROM ImpactData ORDER BY impact_value DESC
SELECT program_name, SUM(impact_value) AS total_impact_value FROM ImpactData GROUP BY program_name
SELECT * FROM ImpactData WHERE impact_value > 100 ORDER BY impact_value DESC, program_name ASC
SELECT program_name, SUM(impact_value) AS total_impact FROM ImpactData GROUP BY program_name
SELECT community_name, impact_metric, AVG(impact_value) AS average_impact FROM ImpactData GROUP BY community_name, impact_metric HAVING AVG(impact_value) > 50
SELECT impact_metric, COUNT(*) AS impact_count FROM ImpactData GROUP BY impact_metric ORDER BY impact_count DESC
SELECT * FROM ImpactData WHERE program_name LIKE 'A%' OR community_name = 'Community A'
SELECT * FROM program_impact;
SELECT program_id, program_name, target_community FROM program_impact ORDER BY program_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM community_feedback WHERE rating > 3;
SELECT program_name, impact_metric FROM program_impact WHERE program_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT community_name, feedback_text FROM community_feedback WHERE feedback_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174001';
SELECT program_name, target_community FROM program_impact;
SELECT * FROM community_feedback WHERE rating > 3;
SELECT program_name, target_community, impact_metric FROM program_impact WHERE program_name LIKE '%education%';

SELECT program_name, target_community, COUNT(program_id) AS total_feedback FROM program_impact LEFT JOIN community_feedback ON program_impact.program_id = community_feedback.program_id GROUP BY program_id;

SELECT program_name, target_community, MAX(rating) AS highest_rating FROM program_impact INNER JOIN community_feedback ON program_impact.program_id = community_feedback.program_id GROUP BY program_id;
SELECT * FROM organizations;
SELECT name, location FROM organizations WHERE id = 5;
SELECT program_name, start_date, end_date FROM programs WHERE program_id = 10;
SELECT * FROM impact_reports WHERE impact_date = '2022-01-01';
SELECT organization_id, COUNT(*) AS report_count FROM programs GROUP BY organization_id;
SELECT * FROM organizations;
SELECT name, location FROM organizations WHERE id = 1;
SELECT program_id, program_name, start_date, end_date FROM programs WHERE organization_id = 2;
SELECT * FROM impact_reports WHERE impact_date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY impact_date DESC;

SELECT organizations.name, impact_reports.impact_description FROM organizations JOIN programs ON organizations.id = programs.organization_id JOIN impact_reports ON programs.program_id = impact_reports.program_id WHERE organizations.location = 'New York';
SELECT * FROM programs ORDER BY program_id DESC;
SELECT program_name, target_community FROM programs WHERE start_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT b.name, b.age, p.program_name FROM beneficiaries b JOIN programs p ON b.program_id = p.program_id;
SELECT volunteer_name, age, role FROM volunteers WHERE gender = 'Female';
SELECT i.metric_name, i.value, p.program_name FROM impact_metrics i JOIN programs p ON i.program_id = p.program_id ORDER BY i.value DESC;
SELECT * FROM programs WHERE program_id = 1;
SELECT program_name, start_date, end_date FROM programs WHERE target_community = 'Education';
SELECT name, age, gender, community FROM beneficiaries WHERE program_id = 3 ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT metric_name, value FROM impact_metrics WHERE program_id = 2 AND value > 1000 ORDER BY value DESC;
SELECT volunteer_name, age, gender, role FROM volunteers WHERE role LIKE '%Coordinator%' OR role LIKE '%Manager%';
SELECT program_id, program_name, start_date, end_date, description FROM programs;
SELECT * FROM communities WHERE location = 'New York';
SELECT program_id, program_name, description FROM programs WHERE start_date > '2021-01-01';
SELECT community_name, population_size FROM communities ORDER BY population_size DESC;
SELECT participant_name, age, gender FROM program_participants WHERE gender = 'Male' OR gender = 'Female';
SELECT * FROM programs;
SELECT program_name, start_date, end_date FROM programs WHERE program_id = 1;
SELECT program_name, description FROM programs WHERE start_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT program_name, community_name, location, population_size FROM programs p JOIN communities c ON p.program_id = c.community_id;

SELECT p.program_name, pp.participant_name, pp.age, c.community_name FROM programs p JOIN program_participants pp ON p.program_id = pp.program_id JOIN communities c ON pp.community_id = c.community_id WHERE pp.age > 18;
